IIROBHOTHSI: ZAYIZOLO, ZANAMHLANJE NEZANGOMSO Ingaba uza kuba khona uBonda ukunceda uDevi de kube ngumnyaka ka2085?Kuza kufuneka silinde sibukele, kodwa akukho kuphika ukuba iirobhothsi zizakuba qelele ngolwazi nkqu kwiminyaka engamashumi amabini anesihlanu ezayo ukususelangoku, ukuya kunyaka ka-2040.Ngubani? Iyintoni irobhothi?Ukuba uthe irobhothi ngumatshini okhangeleka nowenza izintonjengabantu, gqwidi nje ukukekela oku xa ihamba, ukungabi namfaneleko kwelizwilayo, amehlo abhanya-bhanya nathi qhwanya xa ivuliwe irobhothi, ubonakalaubukela iifilimu neenkqubo zikamabona-kude ezininzi.  Kuba, kahle kahle, irobhothi le “yiyo nayiphina imatshini yombane elawulwa yikhompyutha okanye imicwana yeentambo esebenzangombane.” Kakuhle ncam, ayifanelanga kukhangeleka njengomntu gqibi. Yiyo loonto ubungenakho ukuyiqaphela into yokuba sihlala singqongwe ziirobhothsi! Nyhani? Phi?Mamela ke, zikho kwimizi-mveliso, kwimizi-ntengiso, ezifama,ezibhedlele, nkqu nasemakhaya. Zinakho ukukhangeleka njengemitshini eneengaloezinkulu, njengeziyaa zikwimivi-mveliso yeemoto, ezobuchweli, ukuncamathisela iglue nokupeyinta amalungu eemoto. Okanyezisenokubonakala njengeekhamera, njengeziyaa zifumaneka ezibhedlele, nezithiwencaa eludongeni ngeentanjana ezibhityileyo, nezinokusetyenziswa ukuxilongaiingxaki zamathumbu ethu. Ezinye iirobhothsi zikhangeleka njengamacwecwanaazizicaba asisazinge, nasebenza emakhayeni ethu naseziofisini, naziyaa ezinyezivuvuza zifunxa uthuli zicoca iimethi zezindlu zethu xa wonke ubani ngokuhlwaelele. Ezinye zikhangeleka njengeenqwelwana ezincinci nezisetyenziswa empiniokanye kwiindawo ezinobungozi njengemigodi, okanye zindande phezu komhlaba,enyangeni, kwiMars, zithathaimifanekiso zikwaqokelela neesampuliezizithumela kubacwaningi (scientists)ezantsi emhlabeni.
Ndinqwenela buqu ukuba ndikhe ndibone irobhothi!Ukuba wawukhe wayisebenzisa, okanye wayibona ikhompyuthaneeselula ezikumgangatho ophezulu zale mihla, uyibonile irobhothi. Ewe,ziyafumaneka kwezo ndawo zinjalo. Ezinye zazo zide zibe nawo namagama,njengooSiri nooCortana (wawukhe weva ngabo?) Ziyasinceda ukufumana ulwaziolubalulekileyo – izinto ezinceda iiprojekthi zesikolo, iingxelozamagosa-ezendlela (zeziphi iindlela ezinoxinano lweemoto namhlanje? Yeyiphiindlela eyenye esingayisebenzisa ukuphungula olu xinano?), ezolonwabo (iqhubekaphi imuvi entsha kaDeepika Padukone? Kwayeumboniso wayo olandelayo?), nezinye nezinye ke. Zisenokusibhalisela amatikiti ebhasi nawetreyini,zisithengele ukutya, zisixelele ukuba zingaphi na iikhalorizi (calories) zokutya emizimbeni yethu nesiziphunguleyo emvakomdlalo webhola.  Likhangeleka njani ikamva leerobhothsi? Liza kuba njani ilizwengeminyaka yoo-2040, xa sijonge imisebenzi yeerobhothsi? Sisenokungabi nazo iirobhothsi ezihamba ezitalatwenizethu zase-India ngo-2040, kodwa ngokuqinisekileyo siza kube singqongweziirobhothsi zale intlobo okanye enye sibe singayazi thina loo nto.Kusenokwenzeka ukuba zakube zikhona “iirobhothsi” zeemoto eziziqhubayoezitalatweni zethu. Sisenokuba nazo neerobhothi ezincinane kakhulu kwiikhamerazethu ezixokomezelelwayo (contact lenses)ezisinceda ukuthwebula izithombe – akuzudingeka nokuba sizibambe iiselula zethuneekhamera ukuthatha izithombe (kodwa siza kuzithatha njani iiselfi?) Neerobhothsi ezincinane ezibizwaiidrones ziza kube zindandela phezuluziqukeza apha naphaya – zihambisa iileta, imithwalo iikababs, ziphumze abafana abangoomalayisha-mithwalo, nangethembalokuba zakunciphisa nolu xinano lweemoto lungaka ezindleleni! Ngomnya ka-2085, kwiminyakaengama-45 emva koko, Ngubani owaziyo ukuba zakube ziphezu kwantoni iirobhothsi?
Kudala-dala, kwakukho indoda eyayinesilonda esibi emlenzeni. Yayingakwazi ukuma nokuhamba. Le ndoda yayihlala elalini nenkosikazi yayo kunye nabantwana babo.
Esi sibini sasinoonyana abathathu kunye nentombazana enye. Igama lentombazana yayinguNangila. Umsebenzi kaNangila yayikukunakekela uyise. Amakhwenkwe wona ayesebenza emasimini esolusa nemfuyo.
UNangila wayeyintombazana entle. Bonke abantu belali babemthanda futhi bemhlonipha. Abazali bakhe bona babefunela intombi yabo isoka eliqotho. Benza iqhinga elinzima ukuze bafumane eyona ndoda emfaneleyo.
Umntu owayefuna ukutshata noNangila kwakufanele ayokufuna iyeza elalifumaneka echibini elalikufutshane nelali leyo. Eli yeza lalizokupholisa isilonda sikatata kaNangila. Kodwa leli chibi laligcwele iziporho nezithunzela ezinobungozi.
Amanye amadoda azama ukuya kukha eli yeza kodwa abuya elambatha. Amanye amadoda awazange abuye kwa ukubuya kwelo chibi.
UNangila wakhathazeka. Nditsho nabantakwabo babengakwazi ukufika echibini. Ngoko wagqiba ekubeni ayokulikha ngokwakhe eli yeza. Umama wakhe wathi, "Mntwana wam, ucinga ukuba uza kuphumelela na, njengokuba namadoda anamandla ohlulekile?" Kodwa uNangila wayesele esithathile isigqibo, engasenakubuya ngamva.
Endleleni eya echibini, uNangila wadibana nexhegwazana elalithwele inyanda yeenkuni. Walithwalela inyanda yalo ixhegwazana. Ixhegokazi labulela laze lathi kuNangila, "Ndiza kukuxelela indlela onokufikelela ngayo echibini leziporho nento ekufanele uyenze xa ufika khona."
Wathi xa efikelela enyeleni yechibi, uNangila wabona usapho lweziporho lisela yaye lixhentsa. Walinda wabukela. Suke iziporho zabiwa bubuthongo ngasinye ngexesha.
Kwathi xa sele zilele zonke, uNangila wantywilela echibini. Walifumana iyeza waze walifaka epokothweni yakhe. Uthe xa edada ebuyela enyeleni, suke amaza aba made ukumodlula.
Iziporho zazisele zivukile ngelixa uNangila efika enyeleni yechibi. Wayesoyika kodwa wacula ingoma awayeyifundiswe lixhegwazana: Mna, ntombi kaWekesa, Ndiphuma echibini. Ndize apha ngoba amadoda ayoyika ukuza. Utata uyalidinga eli yeza ukunyanga isilonda sakhe. Yiyo le nto ndilapha nje, Endaweni apho abaninzi Boyikayo ukufikelela, Kuba nina niphethe.
Ilizwi likaNangila lalimnandi kangangokuba iziporho zamcela ukuba aziculele aphindaphinde amatyeli amaninzi. Ukucula kwakhe kwenza ukuba iziporho ziphinde zibiwe bubuthongo. Wasuka apho wathi ngqe-e-e-e ukugoduka ephindela elalini yakhe.
Bonke abantu babelindele ukubuya kukaNangila. Emva kokunyanga isilonda sakhe ngeyeza, uyise wakwazi ukuphakama kwakhona. Ilali yonke yalilizela incoma uNangila.
